sec.p:
Potentially relevant datasets deposited in GEO were identified using an advanced query based on the Bioconductor package GEOmetadb and the SQLite database that captures detailed information on the GEO data structure;
https://www.bioconductor.org/packages/release/bioc/html/GEOmetadb.html
66. The search query was designed to retrieve entries where the title and description contained the word Monocyte OR Monocytes, were generated from human samples, using Illumina or Affymetrix commercial platforms. The query result is appended with rich metadata from GEOmetadb that allows for manual filtering of the retrieved collection.
